short_description: The challenge for this round is to make a track using only samples generated with Uhhyou Web Synthesizers.
long_description: Uhhyou Web Synthesizers is a collection of musical synthesizers to render WAVE files, https://ryukau.github.io/UhhyouWebSynthesizers/. Your challenge for this round is to **make a track using only samples generated with Uhhyou Web Synthesizers**.
